OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FThe following charities are also there
OL,7,Fto help.
OL,9,FMind have branches across the region
OL,10,Fproviding support for mental health
OL,11,Fsuch as talking therapies, counselling
OL,12,Fand crisis helplines. You can find
OL,13,Fyour local branch here.
OL,15,FMind's support line can be reached on
OL,16,F0300 102 1234.
OL,18,FThe charity can also signpost to
OL,19,Fresources for under 18s, and can
OL,20,Fprovide legal information and guidance
OL,21,Faround welfare and benefits.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
