OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772892686
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FIf U Care Share promotes emotional
OL,7,Fwellbeing in young people and supports
OL,8,Ffamilies affected by suicide. Call
OL,9,F0191 387 5661.
OL,11,FSamaritans provide confidential, non-
OL,12,Fjudgemental emotional support for
OL,13,Fpeople experiencing feelings of
OL,14,Fdistress or despair. Call 116 123
OL,15,F(freephone, landlines and mobile) or
OL,16,Femail jo@samaritans.org.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
