OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772892686
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FPAPYRUS is the national UK charity
OL,7,Fdedicated to the prevention of young
OL,8,Fsuicide. Call 0800 068 41 41 (Monday
OL,9,Fto Friday 10am-5pm and 7pm-10pm/
OL,10,Fweekends 2pm-5pm), text 07786 209697
OL,11,For email pat@papyrus-uk.org.
OL,13,FCampaign Against Living Miserably
OL,14,F(CALM) is a male suicide prevention
OL,15,Fcharity. Call 0800 585858 (every day
OL,16,F5pm`midnight). A web char service is
OL,17,Falso available.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
