OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1772892686
OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FRethink aims to make sure everyone
OL,7,Fseverely affected by mental illness
OL,8,Fhas a good quality of life. Call 0300
OL,9,F5000 927 (Monday to Friday 10am-2pm,
OL,10,Fnot including bank holidays).
OL,12,FSANE runs a national, out-of-hours
OL,13,Fmental health helpline offering
OL,14,Fspecialist emotional support and
OL,15,Finformation to anyone affected by
OL,16,Fmental illness, including family,
OL,17,Ffriends and Carers. Call 0300 304 7000
OL,18,F(every day 6pm-11pm).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
