OL,3,CContact details for mental health
OL,4,Cservices in the North East
OL,6,FStreetwise provides mental health
OL,7,Fsupport for young people. Call 0191
OL,8,F2305400 or 0191 2305533.
OL,10,FAnxiety UK runs a helpline on weekdays
OL,11,Fbetween 9.30am and 5.30pm. Call 03444
OL,12,F775 774.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
